  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>Your privacy is important to us at LuxeDrive. Here’s how we handle your information.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
          <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
          <p>We collect your name, email, phone number, payment details, rental preferences, and automatically gathered browsing data.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i></div>
          <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>To process bookings and payments</li>
            <li>To send booking confirmations and updates</li>
            <li>To recommend vehicles and offers</li>
            <li>To improve our services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i></div>
          <h3>Sharing of Information</h3>
          <p>We don’t sell or rent your information. Data is shared only with trusted partners for payment processing, customer service, and legal compliance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></div>
          <h3>Data Security</h3>
          <p>We use industry-standard encryption and security protocols, but no online transmission is fully secure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i></div>
          <h3>Your Rights</h3>
          <p>You can request access, updates, or deletion of your data. You may also opt out of marketing communications at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-cookie-bite"></i></div>
          <h3>Cookies</h3>
          <p>We use cookies for better browsing, analytics, and personalization. You can manage cookies in your browser settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i></div>
          <h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
          <p>We may update our Privacy Policy periodically. Updated versions will be posted on this page with the revision date.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text"></i></div>
          <h3>Contact Us</h3>
          <p>Email: info@luxedrive.in</p>
          <p>Phone: +91 98765 43210</p>
          <p>Address: Bandra Kurla Complex, Mumbai</p>
        </div>
      </div>
